    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The reproductive portions of any plant in the division Angiospermae, flowering plants. As popularly used, the term "flower" especially applies when part or all of the reproductive structure is distinctive in color and form.</Note_Text>
